            "type": "canvas",
            "canvasData": "{}",
            "teacherNotes": "### The Motion Verb Challenge\n\nUkrainian motion verbs are famous for being difficult. But they follow logical patterns!\n\n**The core distinction:**\n- **Unidirectional:** One direction, one trip, right now\n- **Multidirectional:** Multiple directions, round trips, habitual"
          }
        ]
      }
